1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 11=

4
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,280
Why did you follow us?

5
00:00:21,879 --> 00:00:23,079
That's the Demon Sect's
Corpsefang Poison Mist.

6
00:00:23,079 --> 00:00:24,399
Everyone, stay alert.

7
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,320
Mr. Murong,

8
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:28,239
an urgent matter
has come up in our sect.

9
00:00:28,239 --> 00:00:29,760
Well, we'll be leaving now.

10
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:30,559
Yes.

11
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:31,960
We should go.

12
00:00:33,439 --> 00:00:34,640
Two of the Demon Sect's
Six Ghost Disciples

13
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:35,960
showed up at once.

14
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:38,759
There'll be bloodshed today.

15
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,159
They're only human.

16
00:00:41,159 --> 00:00:42,200
What's there to fear?

17
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:43,920
As a man of the Dao,

18
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:45,079
keep your heart steady.

19
00:00:45,079 --> 00:00:46,240
Don't let fear run wild.

20
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:46,860
(Surrender)

21
00:00:49,039 --> 00:00:49,799
Coward!

22
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,119
You're

23
00:00:58,479 --> 00:00:59,799
Peng Dasheng?

24
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,320
That's him.

25
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:09,280
You're the master
of the Northern Evil Duo, aren't you?

26
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,640
How did you know?

27
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,599
When I fought them last time,

28
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,760
their sinister aura
felt just like yours.

29
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,480
Then you used the Blood Crow Formation.

30
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:18,760
It wasn't hard to connect the dots.

31
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:19,879
I'm not stupid.

32
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:23,920
Since you're so good at guessing,

33
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:27,239
tell me why I'm here.

34
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:30,359
To avenge your disciples, obviously.

35
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,159
Wrong.

36
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,400
My disciples lacked skill.

37
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:35,239
If they died by your hand,

38
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,480
they had it coming.

39
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:38,680
What truly angers me

40
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,000
is that a nobody like you

41
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,439
killed both of them in a single day.

42
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:45,439
How could I, the Jiuyou Judge,
ever hold my head up after that?

43
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,480
That's some twisted logic.

44
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,959
He doesn't care that his disciples died.

45
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:50,480
He only cares about his pride.

46
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:53,680
I didn't know the Demon Sect
was so obsessed with saving face.

47
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,000
Guess villains are all the same.

48
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,359
Enough.

49
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,400
Answer me.

50
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,519
Will you become my disciple?

51
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:08,439
Your disciple?

52
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,400
Me?

53
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,439
Accept me as your master

54
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:12,879
and join the Demon Sect.

55
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:15,680
Then I'll let the matter drop.

56
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,919
What do you say?

57
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,800
Sir, those were two lives.

58
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,960
You're just letting it go?

59
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,919
They were useless.

60
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,439
Their deaths mean nothing.

61
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:27,759
Answer me.
Will you take me as your master?

62
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,560
I already have a master.

63
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:32,879
And I'm not planning to betray my sect
anytime soon.

64
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,759
But there are plenty
of young talents here.

65
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:35,520
Look.

66
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,400
There are some over there too.

67
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,520
That's more than I can handle.

68
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:45,599
Take him.

69
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,800
There are so many to choose from.

70
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:48,680
Pick one.

71
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,039
One of them should suit you.

72
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:52,159
How did this suddenly
become about choosing a disciple?

73
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,840
You don't understand.

74
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:56,680
Training a top fighter
takes at least eight or ten years.

75
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:58,039
It costs too much time and effort.

76
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,199
Why not buy off a skilled outsider

77
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,199
and put him to work?

78
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,599
The Demon Sect needs fresh blood

79
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:05,599
to keep growing.

80
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,560
No wonder it's lasted this long

81
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:10,080
in the martial world.

82
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,639
Ziting,

83
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,759
how do you know all this?

84
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,039
Well, I...

85
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,840
The Master of Nongxiao Pavilion
raised his son well.

86
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,159
Ziting reads every issue

87
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:20,759
of Sect Strategy from Jianghu Academy.

88
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,599
Right, Ziting?

89
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,400
Insolence!

90
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,280
I offered to take you as my disciple.

91
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,439
I was giving you a chance.

92
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,919
Yet you don't know what's good for you

93
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:30,960
and keep making excuses.

94
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:32,199
Would you rather have a taste

95
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:35,400
of my Netherworld Ruler?

96
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,560
You must be joking.

97
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:41,800
This big saber of mine
isn't so bad either.

98
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,599
Wait.

99
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:45,400
Let me play with him.

100
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:48,159
If you drain him dry,

101
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:51,039
I'll have come all this way for nothing.

102
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,080
He's all yours.

103
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,159
Boy,

104
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,280
if you don't want him as your master,

105
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,080
you can take me instead.

106
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:06,400
Keep me happy,

107
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:09,560
and I'll spare your life.

108
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,839
Old woman,

109
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,160
if you were fifty years younger,

110
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,560
I might actually play along.

111
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:29,600
You brat! How dare you call me old?

112
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:31,480
I'm forever eighteen!

113
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,680
Then fight.

114
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,600
At your age,

115
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,720
you sure talk a lot.

116
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,680
You insolent brat!

117
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:39,040
Die!

118
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,720
Why won't these corpse puppets die?

119
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,199
What makes the Nether Marionette
so formidable

120
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:08,319
is that she turns living men
into corpse puppets.

121
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,759
She chooses strong men in their prime

122
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:12,480
and forces Bloodscale Elixir
down their throats

123
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,959
while they're fully conscious.

124
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,839
It dissolves
the moment it touches blood,

125
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,720
then travels through their meridians
straight to the heart.

126
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:20,399
For a short time, it gives them
a huge boost in inner force.

127
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,399
Even when run through by a blade,

128
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:23,360
they feel no pain.

129
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,480
They won't stop until they die.

130
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,319
There has to be a way to stop them.

131
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,800
The good news is,

132
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,920
once they start attacking,

133
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,959
they won't last long.

134
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,360
The bad news is,

135
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,680
no one has ever survived

136
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,600
that long against them.

137
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,759
Their weak point
is the back of the neck.

138
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,199
Xiao, did you notice?

139
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,959
Dasheng's saber skills

140
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:26,519
have improved greatly
since our last encounter.

141
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:29,480
He's advancing at an astonishing rate.

142
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,759
Given time,

143
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,879
one day,

144
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,120
only the Four Grandmasters

145
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:35,920
may be able to rival him.

146
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,480
Skill matters

147
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,720
in the martial world,

148
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:40,240
but if a man's character is rotten,

149
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,800
none of it matters.

150
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,800
I don't see what's so special about him.

151
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:49,279
The Murong family led the martial
alliance for two terms in a row.

152
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:51,000
Its ranks are filled with heroes

153
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,000
and known far and wide.

154
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:54,680
Countless families lined up

155
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,120
to propose a marriage alliance.

156
00:06:56,839 --> 00:07:00,079
Yet Dasheng rejected the match.

157
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:02,839
His loyalty and refusal to bow to power

158
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:04,839
set him apart from ordinary men.

159
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:08,160
I think he's just stubborn

160
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:09,600
and hopelessly foolish.

161
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:12,240
There are plenty of clever men
in the martial world.

162
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,040
But when life and death are at stake,

163
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:18,360
a fool like him
is exactly the man I'd trust.

164
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:29,040
Amazing!

165
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,600
He did it!

166
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:37,199
Dasheng broke the Demon Sect's

167
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:39,360
Corpse Puppet Formation all by himself.

168
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,439
What a remarkable young man!

169
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:44,079
Such strength,

170
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:45,079
such grace!

171
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,759
Mr. Peng cuts quite a figure,

172
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,960
just like I did in my prime.

173
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:48,720
(Fight to the Death)
Just like I did in my prime.

174
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,600
Oh, please!

175
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,879
Shameless.

176
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,519
Old man.

177
00:07:57,839 --> 00:08:01,199
That brat actually broke
my Corpse Puppet Formation.

178
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,600
Be careful.

179
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,160
Don't underestimate him.

180
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,040
Kill him?

181
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,120
I don't need to lift a finger.

182
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:14,639
Dasheng!

183
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,560
Dasheng!

184
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:33,759
Dasheng!

185
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,159
Peng Dasheng!

186
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:47,519
I, Ziting, pay my respects
to the two Demon Envoys.

187
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,080
You did well.

188
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,559
You helped the Demon Sect
eliminate a major threat.

189
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:52,960
You flatter me, sir.

190
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:55,279
I merely did my part.

191
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:57,879
After this,

192
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:59,639
I'll report your service to Master
and ask that you be rewarded.

193
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,679
Once the Demon Sect
rules the martial world,

194
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:04,360
your family will get the title
of Martial Arts Alliance Leader.

195
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,320
I'm grateful

196
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:08,000
that Master thinks me worthy.

197
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,120
Xiao Ziting,

198
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,519
you defected to the Demon Sect

199
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:11,720
over an empty promise

200
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,200
of becoming
Martial Arts Alliance Leader?

201
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,639
Have you lost your mind?

202
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,440
What do you know?

203
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,519
By seniority and family standing,

204
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:22,320
the title should've gone
to my father long ago.

205
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,879
Had my father not stepped aside,

206
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:25,279
the title never would've gone
to the Murong family.

207
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,799
I'm simply taking back

208
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,279
what always belonged to my family.

209
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,320
How is that wrong?

210
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,039
Xiao Ziting,

211
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,720
you betrayed your fellow martial artists
for your own gain.

212
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,879
Have you no sense of honor left?

213
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,159
In the martial world,

214
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:41,519
strength is everything.

215
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,600
Those who submit prosper.

216
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,840
Those who defy me die.

217
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,600
That's how the world should work.

218
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:49,600
The martial world
you people keep talking about

219
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,799
is nothing
but a lie you tell yourselves.

220
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,679
Everyone, stay calm.

221
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:57,039
Murong Manor is full of experts.

222
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:59,120
The Demon Sect won't have its way.

223
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,879
Mr. Bai,

224
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,879
I'd advise

225
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,720
you to save your breath.

226
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,440
Before I came here,

227
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,679
I had Murong Manor's experts

228
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:09,159
sent to Jiangbei.

229
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,519
Only the old, the weak,

230
00:10:10,519 --> 00:10:12,759
and the wounded remain at the manor.

231
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:14,639
Isn't that right, Mr. Murong?

232
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,440
Mr. Murong, is that...

233
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,799
He's right.

234
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,480
Three days ago, I received a letter
from the Master of Nongxiao Pavilion.

235
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,679
He said the Demon Sect's leader

236
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:25,639
had been spotted in Jiangbei

237
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,559
and asked me to send men
to help destroy the Demon Sect.

238
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:32,840
Most of my best fighters
went to Jiangbei.

239
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,159
They left only yesterday.

240
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:35,440
What?

241
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:50,440
What are you waiting for?

242
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,000
Are you just going to wait here to die?

243
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,279
Sir, before I came,

244
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,200
my father asked me

245
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,840
to deliver a letter to you.

246
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:05,080
He said you had to open it here

247
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,360
to learn his true intentions.

248
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:08,120
Where is it?

249
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,559
Here you are.

250
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:36,360
Ziting!

251
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:46,519
Did you really think
this cheap trick could fool me?

252
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,000
How naive.

253
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:54,080
So you knew all along.

254
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,320
Boy,

255
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,639
we never trusted you.

256
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:02,519
What do you think
of Xiao Ziting's offer to join us?

257
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,559
It's probably a trap.

258
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,120
Accept it.

259
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:10,840
But a dog seeking a new master

260
00:12:11,519 --> 00:12:14,000
must first tear out
its old master's throat.

261
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:20,000
Brilliant.

262
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:25,320
Any last words?

263
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:29,919
We'll see who survives.

264
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,000
No need to call for help.

265
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:55,080
The fighters you stationed
at the estate outside the city

266
00:12:55,679 --> 00:12:58,080
are already nothing but bones.

267
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:58,960
How could this be?

268
00:13:00,159 --> 00:13:01,440
How could this happen?

269
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:06,159
I slipped Bone-Eroding Poison
into their wine.

270
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,559
Then I watched my poisonous worms

271
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:10,960
devour their insides.

272
00:13:11,279 --> 00:13:13,320
The way they writhed on the ground...

273
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:17,320
What a glorious sight!

274
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,320
Sang Wuqi!

275
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,320
I'll kill you!

276
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:31,279
A wet-behind-the-ears boy like you

277
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:33,279
dares challenge me?

278
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,159
Remember this, boy.

279
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:38,200
In the martial world,
the strong make the rules.

280
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:41,720
The weak die.

281
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,720
Let him go!

282
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,720
You're alive?

283
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,200
Dasheng!

284
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,120
Dasheng.

285
00:13:55,759 --> 00:13:57,120
I was too arrogant.

286
00:13:57,679 --> 00:13:59,240
This disaster is all my fault.

287
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:01,919
Dasheng.

288
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,519
Instead of blaming yourself,

289
00:14:12,879 --> 00:14:14,039
do something useful.

290
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,039
Take care of Xiaojiu for me.

291
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,240
I will.

292
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,159
One more thing.

293
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:20,320
Sang Wuqi is the Demon Sect's

294
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,519
second-strongest fighter.

295
00:14:22,639 --> 00:14:24,440
He's several times stronger
than the Northern Evil Duo.

296
00:14:24,759 --> 00:14:25,759
Be very careful.

297
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:32,759
You old fiend.

298
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:36,799
You played dead pretty well, boy.

299
00:14:36,879 --> 00:14:38,759
You should've stayed down.

300
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,840
Why come back just to die for real?

301
00:14:41,679 --> 00:14:44,360
Your voice is more annoying
than a fly buzzing in my ear.

302
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:46,039
You kept me awake.

303
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,399
I'll cut you down first

304
00:14:47,639 --> 00:14:48,799
and get some peace and quiet.

305
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:57,580
♪Come on♪

306
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:02,780
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

307
00:15:04,740 --> 00:15:07,700
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

308
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:10,900
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

309
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:13,980
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

310
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:16,980
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

311
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:20,460
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

312
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:23,700
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

313
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:26,780
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

314
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:29,700
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

315
00:15:30,260 --> 00:15:33,580
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

316
00:15:33,620 --> 00:15:36,620
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

317
00:15:36,660 --> 00:15:42,300
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

318
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:44,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

319
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:47,820
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

320
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:50,940
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

321
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:54,740
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

322
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:57,460
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

323
00:15:58,380 --> 00:16:00,500
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

324
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:03,940
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

325
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:08,260
♪I am my own king♪

326
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:22,900
♪I emerge into the world♪

327
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:24,660
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

328
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:26,020
♪My pride is my trump card♪

329
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:27,820
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

330
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:29,220
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

331
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:30,980
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

332
00:16:30,980 --> 00:16:32,500
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

333
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:34,220
♪I dare to break every rule♪

334
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:35,540
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

335
00:16:35,540 --> 00:16:37,380
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

336
00:16:37,380 --> 00:16:38,620
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

337
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:40,860
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

338
00:16:40,860 --> 00:16:42,380
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

339
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,980
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

340
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:45,580
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

341
00:16:45,580 --> 00:16:47,300
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

342
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:49,020
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

343
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:50,380
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

344
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:52,020
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

345
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,500
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

346
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:55,220
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

347
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:56,820
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

348
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:58,380
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

349
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:02,700
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

350
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:04,860
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

351
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:07,460
♪Let me write the legend♪

352
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:14,900
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

353
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:18,220
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

354
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:20,700
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

355
00:17:20,700 --> 00:17:24,780
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

356
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:27,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

357
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:30,220
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

358
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:33,260
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

359
00:17:33,260 --> 00:17:38,300
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
